"""Prototype: 3D local-max pseudo-centroids as clamp source.

Idea: cells in HCR are punctate, autofluorescence is diffuse.  3D local
maxima filter the first one in and leave the second out — the shallow
tail of peaks is therefore BELOW pia (real cells), not above it
(autofluorescence).  Behaves like centroids in N22's clamp.
"""
